{"_path":"/health/h011","_dir":"health","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"肺腺癌","description":null,"image":null,"sequence":11,"category":"養生防癌","link":null,"head":{"meta":[{"name":"keywords","content":""},{"name":"robots","content":""},{"name":"author","content":""},{"name":"copyright","content":"© 2024 A7新林口 - 社區網站"},{"name":"og:title","content":"健康休閒"}]},"publishedAt":"2025-04-17T00:00:00.000Z","toc":true,"body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"肺腺癌"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"肺腺癌"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"什麼是肺腺癌"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"什麼是肺腺癌？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"肺腺癌（Lung Adenocarcinoma）是肺癌的一種，屬於非小細胞肺癌（NSCLC），起源於肺部腺體細胞（通常位於肺的外圍區域）。它是目前最常見的肺癌類型，特別在非吸菸者、女性及亞洲人群中較為普遍。肺腺癌的特點包括："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"症狀"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：早期可能無明顯症狀，後期可能出現咳嗽、咳血、胸痛、呼吸困難、疲倦或體重減輕。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"危險因素"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：吸菸（包括二手菸）、環境污染（如空氣汙染、PM2.5）、石棉或氡氣暴露、遺傳因素、慢性肺病等。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"診斷"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：透過胸部 X 光、CT 掃描、痰液檢查或活檢確診。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"分期與治療"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：根據分期（I-IV 期），治療包括手術、放療、化療、標靶治療或免疫療法。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"hr","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"如何預防肺腺癌"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"如何預防肺腺癌？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"雖然無法完全避免肺腺癌，但以下措施可顯著降低風險："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ol","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"戒菸與避免二手菸"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"吸菸是肺癌的主要風險因素，戒菸可大幅降低風險（戒菸 10-15 年後，風險接近非吸菸者）。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"避免二手菸或三手菸暴露，特別是在密閉空間。"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"減少環境污染物暴露"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"避免接觸空氣污染嚴重的環境，外出時佩戴 N95 口罩。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"減少接觸石棉、氡氣（檢查家中氡氣濃度）、化學物質（如苯、砷）。"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"健康飲食"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"多攝取富含抗氧化劑的食物，如新鮮蔬果（十字花科蔬菜、莓果）以對抗自由基。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"減少加工食品、紅肉及高溫油炸食物攝取。"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"規律運動"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"每周 150 分鐘中等強度有氧運動（如快走、游泳），增強肺功能及免疫力。"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"定期健康檢查"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"高風險族群（長期吸菸者、家族病史者、55 歲以上）可考慮每年低劑量 CT 篩檢，早期發現異常。"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"管理慢性肺病"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"積極治療慢性阻塞性肺病（COPD）或肺纖維化等疾病，減少併發症風險。"}]}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"hr","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"如何保養針對肺腺癌患者或高風險者"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"如何保養（針對肺腺癌患者或高風險者）？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"若已診斷肺腺癌或屬高風險族群，保養重點在於減緩疾病進展、改善生活品質及支持治療："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ol","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"遵循醫療計畫"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"配合醫囑進行手術、放療、化療、標靶治療或免疫療法，定期追蹤（如 CT、血液檢查）。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"報告任何新症狀（如呼吸困難、持續咳嗽）以調整治療。"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"戒菸與避免刺激物"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"完全戒菸，避免二手菸及空氣污染物，減少肺部刺激。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"使用空氣清淨機，保持室內空氣清潔。"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"營養支持"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"均衡飲食"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：攝取高蛋白食物（如魚、雞蛋、豆類）以支持組織修復，補充維生素 D、Omega-3 脂肪酸。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"抗炎飲食"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：地中海飲食（橄欖油、堅果、蔬果、全穀類）有助減少炎症。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"避免體重流失"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：若治療導致食慾下降，可選擇高熱量、易消化的食物（如奶昔、濃湯），必要時諮詢營養師。"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"呼吸與運動訓練"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"參與肺部復健計畫（如呼吸訓練、胸廓擴張運動）以改善肺功能。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"適度運動（如瑜伽、太極、散步），根據體能調整強度，增強心肺耐力。"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"心理健康"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"肺腺癌診斷可能帶來壓力，建議透過心理諮詢、支持團體或冥想減輕焦慮。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"與家人朋友保持聯繫，尋求情感支持。"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"避免感染"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"接種流感疫苗、肺炎鏈球菌疫苗，降低呼吸道感染風險。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"勤洗手，避免人群密集處，特別在免疫力下降時（如化療期間）。"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"定期追蹤與生活調整"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"每 3-6 個月接受影像學檢查及腫瘤標記（如 CEA）監測。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"避免熬夜，保持規律作息，促進身體修復。"}]}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"hr","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"具體飲食建議"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"具體飲食建議"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"早餐"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：燕麥粥搭配莓果、亞麻籽，配低脂牛奶或無糖豆漿。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"午餐"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：糙米飯、蒸鮭魚、燙菠菜，佐以橄欖油檸檬醬。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"晚餐"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：雞胸肉蔬菜湯、藜麥沙拉（小黃瓜、番茄、鷹嘴豆）。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"點心"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：無鹽堅果、蘋果或奇異果，補充抗氧化劑。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"飲品"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：多喝水、綠茶（含抗氧化劑），避免含糖飲料及酒精。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"hr","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"其他注意事項"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"其他注意事項"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"高風險族群"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：若有 EGFR、ALK 等基因突變家族史，應與醫師討論基因檢測及預防策略。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"環境改善"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：長期居住在空氣污染嚴重地區者，考慮搬遷或使用高效能空氣清淨機。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"謹慎使用補充劑"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：某些補充劑可能干擾治療，服用前需諮詢醫師。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"早期發現關鍵"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：肺腺癌早期診斷（I-II 期）5 年存活率可達 70-90%，因此定期篩檢至關重要。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"透過戒菸、健康生活及定期檢查，可有效降低肺腺癌風險或改善預後。若已確診，積極治療與生活調整能提升生活品質。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"em","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Disclaimer: Grok is not a doctor; please consult one. Don't share information that can identify you."}]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"肺腺癌","depth":2,"text":"肺腺癌","children":[{"id":"什麼是肺腺癌","depth":3,"text":"什麼是肺腺癌？"},{"id":"如何預防肺腺癌","depth":3,"text":"如何預防肺腺癌？"},{"id":"如何保養針對肺腺癌患者或高風險者","depth":3,"text":"如何保養（針對肺腺癌患者或高風險者）？"},{"id":"具體飲食建議","depth":3,"text":"具體飲食建議"},{"id":"其他注意事項","depth":3,"text":"其他注意事項"}]}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:health:h011.md","_source":"content","_file":"health/h011.md","_extension":"md"}